text: Anja Štefan (Rijeka, 3 August 1988) is a Croatian snowboarder. Most recently she won the silver medal in the Slopestyle at the 2010–11 FIS Snowboard World Cup. == External links == *FIS profile *CROski profile Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Croatian female snowboarders Category:Sportspeople from Rijeka
